This project recreates a production-level documentation landing interface inspired by modern SaaS documentation platforms.

Built completely using core frontend technologies without any frameworks to strengthen layout fundamentals.

#ğŸš€ Why This Project?

Instead of directly copying UI, this project was built to:

Understand real product UI structure

Practice spacing, hierarchy, and readability

Implement modern glass UI effects

Build pixel-accurate layouts manually

Simulate real-world frontend workflow

